summary: Another set of ECE presets. Nord, High Elf, and Dark Elf
descriptionHtml:
Another set of ECE presets. Nord, High Elf, and Dark Elf

Check out the first set [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59499/?tab=1&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmoddescription%2F%3Fid%3D59499%26preview%3D&pUp=1]HERE[/url]

You must have the latest version of "Enhanced Character Edit" mod to use this.
The Elvan presets require "SG Elven Race Patch", located under "optional files" on the SG Female Textures Renewal mod page.Â 

Unzip the folder and add files to: "Documents/games/skyrim/CME_save" folder

Face mods I used for the screenshots were:
1. Seductive Lips HD
2. SG Hair Pack 268 by HelloSanta (Google it)
3. The Eyes Of Beauty
4. ApachiiSkyHair5. SG Female Eyebrows
6. SG Female Textures Renewal

Use these mods to make them look like the ones in the screenshot
